{"tid":2343485,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"消防員去年旺角警民衝突管有4支汽油彈 與另兩人同還柙 1月15日判刑","createTime":"2020-12-28T03:57:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T04:29:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"04d6adeab142f4ba58b7f7f6d5e6e1621909fa2a","tid":2343485,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T03:57:22.000Z","msg":"已婚消防員去年11月10日被指在旺角警民衝突中管有4支汽油彈及拒捕，被捕後一度還柙逾半年，錯過幼子出生，亦未能照顧患抑鬱妻子，至今年5月始獲准保釋。他今於區域法院承認管有物品意圖摧毀或損壞他人財產、抗拒警務人員、管有違禁武器及非法集結等共五罪，同案另有學生及銀行職員認罪。三人須還柙至下月15日判刑。<br />\n<br />\n控罪指他於去年11月10日在彌敦道與山東街一帶，管有4支汽油彈、一支鐵筆、一個鐵鎚、一把彈簧刀及無線傳聲器，抗拒執行職責的警務人員X，以及參與非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/EDAIRQKSNNF73OMQABZZN3DMHE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FEDAIRQKSNNF73OMQABZZN3DMHE%2F&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjd8lSugA1I0CCabXjLbCjl00%3D&h=4d028348\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201228%2FEDAIRQKSNNF73OMQABZZN3DMHE%2F&h=5dc03761\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201228/EDAIRQKSNNF73OMQABZZN3DMHE/</a>"},{"pid":"c5bb493b115078fd52191fb7b1dd384bb7a19faa","tid":2343485,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cc2fc01b58013c1cdaa0db4f5ad95a944700ae4a","tid":2343485,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c5bb493b115078fd52191fb7b1dd384bb7a19faa","tid":2343485,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T03:57:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedB